---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ShapeFooter from "../../components/ShapeFooter.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Program Partner NocoBase - Tumbuhkan bisnis Anda bersama NocoBase"
  description="Bergabunglah dengan program partner NocoBase. Dapatkan komisi dari penjualan kanal dan pertahankan 100% pendapatan layanan Anda. Dua model fleksibel untuk integrator, konsultan, dan penyedia layanan."
  keywords="NocoBase partner, program partner, partner kanal, partner layanan, reseller, integrator sistem"
>
  <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 text-center"><div class="title-heading"><span class="badge bg-soft-primary mb-3">Program Partner</span><h1 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">Kembangkan bisnis Anda<br/>bersama NocoBase</h1><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted">Dua model kerja sama yang fleksibel untuk distribusi, implementasi, atau keduanya. Kita tumbuh bersama.</p><div class="mt-4 pt-2"><a href="mailto:partner@nocobase.com" class="btn btn-primary me-3"><i class="uil uil-envelope me-1"></i>Hubungi kami</a><a href="#partnership-models" class="btn btn-outline-primary"><i class="uil uil-arrow-down me-1"></i>Pelajari lebih lanjut</a></div></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="partnership-models">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12"><div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2"><h4 class="title mb-4">Dua model kemitraan yang fleksibel</h4><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Pilih salah satu atau kombinasikan keduanya untuk memaksimalkan pendapatan</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded h-100 p-4"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"><div class="icons text-start me-3"><i class="uil uil-store rounded h3 mb-0 text-primary"></i></div><h5 class="mb-0">Distribusi kanal</h5></div><p class="text-muted">Promosikan dan jual produk NocoBase untuk mendapatkan komisi berdasarkan pertumbuhan penjualan Anda.</p><ul class="list-unstyled"><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Komisi bertingkat</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Akumulasi jangka panjang</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Dukungan penjualan dan materi tersedia</span></li></ul></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded h-100 p-4"><div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"><div class="icons text-start me-3"><i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0 text-primary"></i></div><h5 class="mb-0">Layanan implementasi</h5></div><p class="text-muted">Tawarkan deployment, kustomisasi, integrasi, dan pelatihan untuk menghasilkan pendapatan berbasis proyek.</p><ul class="list-unstyled"><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Anda mempertahankan 100% pendapatan layanan</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Bebas menentukan model layanan Anda</span></li><li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3"><i class="uil uil-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i><span>Peluang yang diprioritaskan di level lebih tinggi</span></li></ul></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12"><div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2"><h4 class="title mb-4">Bagaimana kami mendukung Anda</h4><p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">Sumber daya dan dukungan untuk membantu partner bertumbuh bersama NocoBase</p></div></div></div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-file-alt h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Dukungan penjualan</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Materi penjualan, konten, dan referensi</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-headphones h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Dukungan teknis</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Kanal dukungan khusus untuk partner</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-users-alt h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Referral</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Prospek yang diteruskan dari NocoBase</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2"><div class="card border-0 text-center features feature-clean course-feature p-4 shadow h-100"><div class="icons text-center"><i class="uil uil-award h1 text-primary"></i></div><div class="content mt-4"><h5>Otorisasi brand</h5><p class="text-muted mt-2">Sertifikat resmi dan peluang co-marketing</p></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-12 text-center"><h4 class="title mb-4">Siap menjadi partner?</h4><p class="text-muted para-desc mx-auto mb-4">Bergabunglah dengan ekosistem partner teknologi yang terus berkembang bersama NocoBase.</p></div></div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10"><div class="card border-0 shadow rounded overflow-hidden"><iframe src="https://service-en.nocobase.com/public-forms/rl8c0cnkyzx" style="width: 100%; min-height: 700px; border: none;" loading="lazy"></iframe></div></div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ShapeFooter />
</Layout>
